snippet.textDisplay:
🌸 Sahih Hadith:
The Prophet ﷺ said:

> “Indeed, Allah has ninety-nine names, one hundred minus one; whoever memorizes them will enter Paradise.”
— Sahih al-Bukhari (2736), Sahih Muslim (2677)



And yes — to reach Jannah, it’s also necessary to avoid major sins (kabirah gunah).
Allah says:

> “If you avoid the major sins which you are forbidden, We will forgive your minor sins and admit you into Paradise.”
— Surah An-Nisa 🤍




---
